  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures or NANTES - Charts 19-1, 19-2, 19-3 from Jeppesen GSPRM 2017. <br>To which risk should you pay special attention?</p>",
  "options": {
    "a": "<div>Increased traffic of gliders and microlights has to be expected.</div>",
    "b": "Runway incursions can occur, because the holding point is located at a great distance from the runway.",
    "c": "<div>A lighted obstacle in front of threshold 03 might be mistaken for the aerodrome beacon.</div>",
    "d": "East traffic circuits should be preferred for noise abatement reasons."
  },
  "correctOption": "b",
